OL,3,CJersey prison needed temporary
OL,4,Cexpansion to cope with demand last year
OL,6,FJersey's prison faced higher demand in
OL,7,F2024, as the number of people
OL,8,Fincarcerated in La Moye increased.
OL,10,FThe service was under extra pressure
OL,11,Fas it dealt with a total of 337
OL,12,Fcustodies, which works out to an
OL,13,Faverage of 12% more inmates per day.
OL,15,FDaily average occupancy also rose to
OL,16,F77% from 69% across 2024, peaking at
OL,17,F88% in December.
OL,19,FThe pressures were most felt within
OL,20,Fthe vulnerable prisoner accommodation
OL,21,Funit.
