OL,3,CJersey prison needed temporary
OL,4,Cexpansion to cope with demand last year
OL,6,FIt was full at one point in November
OL,7,F2024, meaning officers had to
OL,8,Ftemporarily expand it to cope with
OL,9,Fdemand.
OL,11,FThe unit usually has a maximum
OL,12,Fcapacity of 59 prisoners, but it
OL,13,Fneeded four extra beds to cover the
OL,14,Fshortfall.
OL,16,FGoing forward, the prison says they
OL,17,Fwant to focus on better support to
OL,18,Freduce reoffending, which would help
OL,19,Ftackle how many people end up back
OL,20,Finside.
